results.name: 30L Waterproof mission backpack 1.0
results.description:
A small backpack or pouch for your ballistic plate.

Can hold one ballistic panel & plate and one hydration system.
Can be attached on the back of the “strap on” plate carrier with I-bars or with the velcro bands through the bands on the back of the yoke on the “Strap on”..
MOLLE bands on the outside so you can attach other pouches on it.
Velcro patches on the front  for name and unit signs.
The bottom of the plate carrier can be opened to insert plates, panels and bladders..
Velcro secured openings in the top for cables or a hydration tube.

results.name: 50 mm buckle adapter set
results.description:
50 mm side release buckles for leg panels.
We use Velcro in our constructions. For users who prefer side release buckles on the leg straps,  we  have developed this adapter set.
Put the male side release buckles on the elastic leg straps.
The Velcro closes around the square ring with the female side release buckle.

results.name: 55L Duffel bag -17
results.description:
Duffel bag and backpack in one.
Padded handles works as shoulder pads also.
Very large opening that makes it easy to see inside the bag.
Two side compartments big enough for your helmet.
One zipped small inside compartment in the flap. One grab handle in each end.
Three windows and one large Velcropatch for patches.

Loop Velcro fabric on parts of the interior so you can attach our insert pockets to get really organized.

 

The Duffel bag is generally accepted as hand luggage for the cabin when flying.

Volume: 55L

results.name: 6L Funny pack
results.description:
This is a versatile bag for many uses, also developed with Tactical Combat Causalty Care (TCCC) in mind.

For the group medic or the technician who wants to carry the required equipment around the waist, on the back or attached to the back pack.
Outside Velcro stripes so that you can attach your markings. MOLLE webbing.

One big compartment with 2 detachable inside walls.

One small and zipped outside compartment.

Fits:
Medical supplies, personal or technical equipment, e.g camera gear. The Funny pack can also serve as a smaller personal back pack.

Fits on:
Around the waist, over a shoulder or crossbody, attached to the 90L/120L back packs or many of our other back packs.

Volume: 6L

Product sheet:S-28-01291, Funny pack -18, 2020A
